 177:src/main.cpp  **** // ŌöĆŌöĆ Voice 3: rich power-chord bass with mixed waveforms + huge filter sweep ŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆ
 178:src/main.cpp  **** //   Mixed shapes for body: saw root (harmonic-rich), square fifth (hollow), a
 179:src/main.cpp  **** //   clean sine sub (tight low end), saw octave on top. Starts dark, then
 180:src/main.cpp  **** //   pressure opens the cutoff dramatically (13 octaves) with high resonance ŌĆö
 181:src/main.cpp  **** //   a vocal, acid-style "wow" as you press harder.
