 196:src/main.cpp  **** // ŌöĆŌöĆ Voice 4: clean sine organ / flute (a melodic, non-bass departure) ŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌö
 197:src/main.cpp  **** //   Pure sine oscillators stacked like organ drawbars: octave-down body, root,
 198:src/main.cpp  **** //   octave-up air, plus a second osc tuned a hair sharp (1.005├Ś) for a slow,
 199:src/main.cpp  **** //   warm chorus shimmer instead of a chord. Higher register than the basses, a
